<p>The 15% referral fee is steeper than Etsy's 6.5% or Swapedly's 10%, and the Amazon environment is relentlessly price-competitive. You're also at the mercy of Amazon's policies and the looming threat that Amazon might create a competing product if yours sells well enough. It happens.</p>

